description: A racer from Teesside in northern England died after losing control of his BMW, an inquest hears.
title: Daley Mathison: Isle of Man TT competitor's death ruled 'tragic' accident
title_page: Daley Mathison: Isle of Man TT competitor's death ruled 'tragic' accident - BBC News
maintext: Coroner Jayne Hughes said it was "shocking" that marshals had to resort to using cement dust to put out the blaze, although she noted the racer did not die due to the fire.
